# The New Fuse - Safe Reset Procedures

## Overview
**⚠️ IMPORTANT**: The original reset script contained dangerous operations and incorrect paths. 
This has been replaced with safe procedures specific to The New Fuse project.

## Safe Reset Commands

### Complete Development Reset (Recommended)
```bash
#!/bin/bash
echo "🔄 Starting safe development reset..."

# Stop running processes safely
pkill -f "turbo\|vite\|yarn dev" || true

# Clean build artifacts and cache
yarn clean
rm -rf .turbo node_modules/.cache
rm -rf packages/*/dist apps/*/dist chrome-extension/dist

# Reinstall dependencies
yarn install

# Rebuild project
yarn build

echo "✅ Safe reset complete!"
```

### Quick Cache Clear
```bash
